<h1 id='relevant-contents-of-available-assets-in-the-accounts'>Relevant Contents Of Available Assets In The Accounts</h1><h2 id='retrieve-user-39-s-assets'>Retrieve User&#39;s Assets</h2>
<p>API Key Permission：Read</p>

<p>Check the balance of designated account, supports the following accounts：</p>

<p><strong>HTTP Request</strong></p>

<ul>
<li>GET /api/v2/balance.query</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Request Parameter</strong></p>

<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Name of Parameter</th>
<th>Required or not</th>
<th>Type</th>
<th>Description</th>
<th>Default Value</th>
<th>Range of Parameter</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>api_key</td>
<td>true</td>
<td>string</td>
<td>The API KEY Requested By The User</td>
<td></td>
<td></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>sign</td>
<td>true</td>
<td>string</td>
<td>The Signature Value of the requested string</td>
<td></td>
<td></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>assets</td>
<td>true</td>
<td>json array</td>
<td>The array of token symbol, blank array means retrieve all token assets</td>
<td></td>
<td></td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>

<p><strong>Response Data</strong></p>

<blockquote>
<p>Response:</p>
</blockquote>
