<h3 id='http-request'>HTTP Request</h3>
<p><code>POST /balance.history</code></p>
<h3 id='request-parameter'>Request Parameter</h3>
<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Name of Parameter</th>
<th>Required Or Not</th>
<th>Type</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>api_key</td>
<td>Yes</td>
<td>string</td>
<td>The API KEY Requested By The User</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>sign</td>
<td>Yes</td>
<td>string</td>
<td>The signature value of the requested string</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>asset</td>
<td>Yes</td>
<td>string</td>
<td>Name of assets，For example：&quot;BTC&quot;,&quot;ETH&quot; etc.，&quot;&quot;means the names of all assets</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>business</td>
<td>Yes</td>
<td>string</td>
<td>Name of business，如：&quot;deposit&quot; or &quot;trade&quot;，&quot;&quot;means the names of all businesses</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>start_time</td>
<td>Yes</td>
<td>Integer(64 digit without symbol)</td>
<td>Starting Time(Second)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>end_time</td>
<td>Yes</td>
<td>Integer(64 digit without symbol)</td>
<td>Ending Time(second)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>offset</td>
<td>Yes</td>
<td>Integer(32 Digit)</td>
<td>Offset position, if set as 0, it means all transaction records starting from the latest transaction to the earliest transaction, the total number of transactions cannot be greater than limit; if set as 1, it means the number of all transaction records starting from the second latest transaction to the earliest transaction cannot be greater than limit; and so on</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>

<p>limit         |Yes              | Integer(32 Digit)        |Maximum number of transactions returned</p>
