<tr>
<th>Name of Paramter</th>
<th>Required or Not</th>
<th>Type</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>api_key</td>
<td>Yes</td>
<td>string</td>
<td>The API KEY Requested By The User</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>

<aside class="notice">
   assets — Blank array means retrieve all token assets
</aside>
